_sText:
Hey, thanks for taking the time to look at this.


I made this map after my friend, Paulendy, told me he was making a fightyard map of his own. I encourage you to go over and take a look at it.

http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/110135

Anyway, this took me a day and a bit to create and troubleshoot. It works pretty well with bots, with a slightly altered navigation mesh.

Please do give me relevant feedback. This is my first proper release, so tips are very welcome.


THANKYOU!
